'''2020年法國網球公開賽'''為第124屆[[法國網球公開賽|法國網球公開賽]]，是[[职业网球联合会|ATP]]/[[国际女子网球协会|WTA]]的其中一站，為2020年賽季[[網球大滿貫|網球大滿貫]]第三站及最後一站比賽。本屆賽事的正賽於2020年9月27日至10月11日在[[法國|法國]][[巴黎|巴黎]][[羅蘭·加洛斯球場|羅蘭·加洛斯球場]]舉行，場地為紅土，總獎金為38,000,000歐元。

该比赛原本是2020年的第二项网球大满贯赛事。然而受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，主办方决定将该届法网延期至9月底至10月上半月进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theweek.in/news/sports/2020/06/18/french-open-postponed-by-another-week-to-start-on-sep-27-with-fans.html|title=French Open postponed by another week, to start on Sep 27 with fans|publisher=The Week|date=2020-06-18|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629074044/https://www.theweek.in/news/sports/2020/06/18/french-open-postponed-by-another-week-to-start-on-sep-27-with-fans.html|archivedate=2020-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管2020年9月底时，法国正经历[[2019冠狀病毒病法國疫情|第二波疫情]]，该届比赛仍然延期后的安排开赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/roland-garros-prepares-to-plow-through-europes-second-wave-11601200800|title=Roland-Garros Prepares to Plow Through Europe's Second Wave|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=2020-09-27|accessdate=2020-10-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006121905/https://www.wsj.com/articles/roland-garros-prepares-to-plow-through-europes-second-wave-11601200800|archivedate=2020-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

赛事主办方针对此次疾病大流行出台了一些应对措施以防止感染扩大。观众方面，主办方决定取消资格赛阶段的现场观众，并对正赛期间现场观赛的观众数量做了一些限制，主办方原定每天开放最多11500名观众在现场观赛，然而比赛开赛数日前，因法国国内第二波疫情的暴发，主办方进一步将每天允许的现场观众人数压缩至1000人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://au.sports.yahoo.com/roland-garros-braced-crowd-limit-193336528.html|title=Roland Garros braced for crowd limit of 1,000 due to Covid-19|publisher=[[法新社|Agence-France Presse]]|date=2020-09-23|accessdate=2020-09-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927063214/https://au.sports.yahoo.com/roland-garros-braced-crowd-limit-193336528.html|archivedate=2020-09-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，所有11岁以上的观众在比赛场地内必须戴上口罩，主办方也会在场地内配备一定数量的消毒液供观众消除手上的细菌及病毒<ref name="espn20201005">{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/tennis/story/_/id/29955986/how-2020-french-open-protocols-differ-us-open|title=How the 2020 French Open's protocols differ from those of the US Open|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2020-09-25|accessdate=2020-10-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005191642/https://www.espn.com/tennis/story/_/id/29955986/how-2020-french-open-protocols-differ-us-open|archivedate=2020-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>；项目设置方面，该届比赛的成年组混合双打比赛、传奇组比赛及青少年组单打项目资格赛均被取消<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.24matins.fr/topnews/sport/roland-garros-le-stade-divise-en-trois-11-500-spectateurs-au-maximum-1224828|script-title=fr:Roland-Garros : Le stade divisé en trois, 11 500 spectateurs au maximum|publisher=24 Matins|date=2020-09-07|accessdate=2020-10-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003172846/https://www.24matins.fr/topnews/sport/roland-garros-le-stade-divise-en-trois-11-500-spectateurs-au-maximum-1224828|archivedate=2020-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>；个人防护方面，所有参赛选手及随行人员必须在主办方指定的酒店居住<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.japantimes.co.jp/sports/2020/09/22/tennis/roland-garros-coronavirus/|title=Rebooted Roland Garros struggles to escape shadow of coronavirus|publisher=[[日本时报|The Japan Times]]|date=2020-09-22|accessdate=2020-10-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923035921/https://www.japantimes.co.jp/sports/2020/09/22/tennis/roland-garros-coronavirus/|archivedate=2020-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在除比赛、训练等以外的场合戴上口罩，及按要求接受[[2019冠状病毒病检测|病毒检测]]<ref name="espn20201005"/>，检测结果阳性的选手必须放弃参加比赛，而与病毒检测阳性人士有密切接触的选手也必须放弃比赛并接受隔离<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/tennis/five-players-out-of-french-open-qualifying-due-to-covid-19/story-f2DpBjET7dzeawbNofiChJ.html|title=Five players out of French Open qualifying due to COVID-19|publisher=Hindustan Times|date=2020-09-21|accessdate=2020-10-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006064110/https://www.hindustantimes.com/tennis/five-players-out-of-french-open-qualifying-due-to-covid-19/story-f2DpBjET7dzeawbNofiChJ.html|archivedate=2020-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

为了帮助有需要的选手度过疫情肆虐的困难时期，主办方提升了较早阶段淘汰选手的奖金，并降低了高排名选手的奖金<ref name="espn20201005"/>。

[[拉斐爾·拿度|拉斐爾·拿度]]在男子单打决赛中直落三盘击败[[諾瓦克·喬科維奇|諾瓦克·喬科維奇]]，成功卫冕法网冠军的同时也获得自己职业生涯的第20个大满贯男单冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/tennis/story/_/id/30090795/rafael-nadal-deserves-all-accolades-2020-french-open-victory|title=Rafael Nadal deserves all the accolades of his 2020 French Open victory|publisher=ESPN|date=2020-10-11|accessdate=2020-10-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031043903/https://www.espn.com/tennis/story/_/id/30090795/rafael-nadal-deserves-all-accolades-2020-french-open-victory|archivedate=2020-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。女子单打方面，[[伊加·斯維亞特克|伊加·斯維亞特克]]以2比0爆冷击败[[索菲亞·科寧|索菲亞·科寧]]，成为历史上首位获得大满贯冠军的波兰选手，以及1992年以来最年轻的法网女单冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theaustralian.com.au/sport/tennis/iga-swiatek-wins-french-open-to-become-polands-first-grand-slam-singles-champion/news-story/abeaaf1dfb7729b34cd12f98675faf9a|title=Iga Swiatek wins French Open to become Poland's first Grand Slam singles champion|publisher=The Australian|date=2020-10-11|accessdate=2020-10-11|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201011020146/https://www.theaustralian.com.au/sport/tennis/iga-swiatek-wins-french-open-to-become-polands-first-grand-slam-singles-champion/news-story/abeaaf1dfb7729b34cd12f98675faf9a|archivedate=2020-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

